1. *Razlike* između ovih proizvoda su minimalne. (The *differences* between these products are minimal.)
2. Ne mogu da pronađem *razlike* između ova dva teksta. (I can't find any *differences* between these two texts.)
3. Moramo da istaknemo *razlike* između ove i one opcije. (We need to highlight the *differences* between this option and that one.)
4. Kada uporedimo ova dva automobila, vidimo mnoge *razlike*. (When we compare these two cars, we see many *differences*.)
5. Treba da prihvatimo *razlike* među ljudima i poštujemo ih. (We should accept the *differences* among people and respect them.)
6. Naučite da cenite *razlike* koje postoje između kultura. (Learn to appreciate the *differences* that exist between cultures.)
7. *Razlike* u mišljenju često mogu dovesti do zanimljivih diskusija. (*Differences* in opinion can often lead to interesting discussions.)
8. Želimo da napravimo anketu kako bismo saznali koje *razlike* ljudi vide između ovih dva proizvoda. (We want to conduct a survey to find out which *differences* people see between these two products.)
9. Postoje *razlike* u našim stavovima o tome šta treba uraditi. (There are *differences* in our opinions about what needs to be done.)
10. Moraćemo da rešimo ove *razlike* pre nego što nastavimo dalje. (We'll have to resolve these *differences* before we can move forward.)